summary: Easily manage and switch between UP TO 5 ENB profiles!
descriptionHtml:
The ultimate way to switch between ENB profiles. Very simple to use and user friendly. No longer do you have to download, redownload, or manually install and uninstall ENB profiles. This tool lets you save [color=#1E90FF][b]up to 5 different enb profiles[/b][/color], all with their own d3d9.dll, sweetFX, and even SMAA, and switch which one you are using with the click of a button. This is the first version, so expect better functionality and more options in the future --- and PLEASE report any bugs!


[color=Green][b]UPDATES:[/b][/color]

   -[b]Version 2.0:[/b] - numerous bug fixes. Can now use if your Skyrim is not installed on C:\\

   -[b]Version 2.1:[/b] - General bug fixes; Bug fixes regarding non-default directories; Now supports the FXAA injection files in the ENB profile.

   -[b]Version 2.2:[/b] - Reworked directory selection code, shouldn\'t cause any more problems.

   -[b]Version 2.3 ([color=Green]current[/color]):[/b] - Numerous bug fixes


-------------------------------------------------------------------










[size=4][b]Check out my other utilities![/b][/size]

------------------------------------------------



[b]REQUIRES .NET FRAMEWORK 4.5 ; I\'m sure you already have it.[/b]
